<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>뇌 기능 기반 미니게임 웹</title>
    <style>
         :root {
            --bg: #ecf4fd;
            --panel: #f7fbff;
            --card: #ffffff;
            --line: #cfe0f5;
            --text: #35506b;
            --sub: #6c86a0;
            --btn: #d8ebff;
            --btn-hover: #c8e1fb;
            --btn-strong: #bfdcff;
            --good: #dff6e8;
            --warn: #fff1cf;
            --soft-blue: #d9ecff;
            --soft-purple: #eee4ff;
            --soft-pink: #ffe5ef;
            --soft-mint: #def7f0;
            --soft-yellow: #fff5d9;
            --shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(79, 117, 157, 0.10);
            --radius: 20px;
        }
        
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box
        }
        
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: "Malgun Gothic", "Apple SD Gothic Neo", sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
        }
        
        button,
        input,
        select {
            font-family: inherit;
        }
        
        .app {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        
        .topbar {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 30;
            background: rgba(236, 244, 253, 0.94);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
            padding: 14px 18px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 12px;
        }
        
        .brand {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        
        .brain-badge {
            width: 42px;
            height: 42px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dbeeff, #f3e8ff);
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            font-size: 22px;
        }
        
        .top-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .btn {
            border: none;
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 11px 15px;
            background: var(--btn);
            color: var(--text);
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            transition: .18s ease;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            background: var(--btn-hover);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
        
        .btn.strong {
            background: var(--btn-strong) !important;
        }
        
        .btn.ghost {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            box-shadow: none;
        }
        
        .screen {
            width: min(1360px, 96vw);
            margin: 20px auto 28px;
            display: none;
        }
        
        .screen.active {
            display: block;
        }
        
        .welcome {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1.15fr .85fr;
            gap: 18px;
        }
        
        .panel {
            background: var(--panel);
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            padding: 22px;
        }
        
        .hero {
            min-height: 430px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 16px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(255, 255, 255, .95), rgba(255, 255, 255, .55) 40%, rgba(255, 255, 255, .15)), linear-gradient(135deg, #dfeeff 0%, #f7ecff 55%, #e8fff6 100%);
        }
        
        .hero h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 40px;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        
        .hero p {
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--sub);
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-size: 17px;
        }
        
        .hero-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        
        .mini-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 14px;
        }
        
        .mini-card {
            background: var(--card);
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 16px;
        }
        
        .mini-card h3 {
            margin: 0 0 8px;
            font-size: 17px;
        }
        
        .mini-card p {
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--sub);
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .main-layout {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1.18fr .82fr;
            gap: 20px;
            align-items: start;
            transition: all 0.4s ease-in-out;
        }
        
        body.brain-hidden .brain-panel {
            display: none;
        }
        
        body.brain-hidden .main-layout {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
        
        .brain-panel {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .section-title {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }
        
        .section-title h2 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        
        .section-title p {
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--sub);
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .brain-stage {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 660px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(255, 255, 255, .85), rgba(255, 255, 255, .4) 35%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 80%), linear-gradient(180deg, #f8fbff, #edf5fd);
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px dashed #d3e4f5;
        }
        
        .brain-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: contain;
            display: block;
            user-select: none;
            -webkit-user-drag: none;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 12px 18px rgba(85, 112, 144, 0.14));
        }
        
        .brain-svg {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }
        
        .region {
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: fill .15s ease, opacity .15s ease, stroke .15s ease;
            stroke: rgba(89, 120, 154, .38);
            stroke-width: 2.2;
            fill: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        }
        
        .region:hover {
            fill: rgba(188, 218, 255, 0.28);
        }
        
        .region.active {
            fill: rgba(176, 214, 255, 0.46);
            stroke: rgba(69, 117, 168, .85);
            stroke-width: 3;
        }
        
        .region.dimmed {
            opacity: .16;
        }
        
        .label-pill {
            position: absolute;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .88);
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            pointer-events: none;
            color: var(--text);
            display: none;
        }
        
        .label-pill.show {
            display: block;
        }
        
        .brain-help {
            margin-top: 14px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .tag {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            color: var(--sub);
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .right-column {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 18px;
        }
        
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 12px;
        }
        
        .stat-card {
            background: var(--card);
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 16px;
        }
        
        .stat-card .label {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--sub);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .stat-card .value {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 800;
        }
        
        .detail-stats {
            display: grid;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 14px;
        }
        
        .detail-row {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 14px;
        }
        
        .detail-row-head {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 10px;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .detail-meta {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--sub);
        }
        
        .detail-meta div {
            background: #f7fbff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #e3eef8;
        }
        
        .game-panel .game-shell {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 22px;
            min-height: 420px;
        }
        
        .game-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }
        
        .game-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 800;
        }
        
        .subline {
            color: var(--sub);
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .inline-controls {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }
        
        .select,
        .text-input {
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            color: var(--text);
            min-width: 120px;
        }
        
        .center-box {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 14px;
            min-height: 180px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .big-number,
        .big-word {
            font-size: 52px;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            color: #476583;
        }
        
        .answer-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
        .quiz-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 92px);
            gap: 12px;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }
        
        .quiz-cell {
            width: 92px;
            height: 92px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 18px;
            background: var(--soft-blue);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            font-size: 30px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: .16s ease;
        }
        
        .quiz-cell:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
        
        .reaction-box {
            width: min(100%, 360px);
            min-height: 180px;
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            border-radius: 22px;
            border: 2px dashed #d5e5f4;
            background: #f8fbff;
            margin: 10px auto 0;
            padding: 18px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .visual-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 94px);
            gap: 12px;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }
        
        .visual-card {
            width: 94px;
            height: 94px;
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            font-size: 34px;
            background: #fff;
            transition: .16s ease;
        }
        
        .visual-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
        
        .visual-card.selected {
            background: var(--btn-strong);
            border-color: #94bde8;
        }
        
        .temporal-choice.selected {
            background: var(--btn-strong) !important;
            border-color: #94bde8 !important;
        }
        
        .footer-note {
            margin-top: 14px;
            color: var(--sub);
            font-size: 13px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .hidden {
            display: none !important;
        }
        
        .modal-backdrop {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background: rgba(39, 59, 85, .28);
            display: none;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            z-index: 50;
            padding: 16px;
        }
        
        .modal-backdrop.show {
            display: flex;
        }
        
        .modal {
            width: min(520px, 96vw);
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 22px 50px rgba(51, 75, 103, .22);
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .modal h3 {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
            font-size: 22px;
        }
        
        .modal p {
            color: var(--sub);
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .modal-grid {
            display: grid;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 14px;
        }
        
        .setting-item {
            background: #f8fbff;
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 14px;
        }
        
        .setting-item label {
            display: block;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .status-banner {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding: 12px 14px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            background: var(--warn);
            color: #7a6531;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: none;
        }
        
        .status-banner.show {
            display: block;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 1100px) {
            .welcome,
            .main-layout {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .brain-stage {
                min-height: 520px;
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 700px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 31px;
            }
            .stats-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
            .detail-meta {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
            .quiz-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 78px);
            }
            .quiz-cell {
                width: 78px;
                height: 78px;
            }
            .visual-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 80px);
            }
            .visual-card {
                width: 80px;
                height: 80px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="app">
        <header class="topbar">
            <div class="brand">
                <div class="brain-badge">🧠</div>
                <div>뇌 기능 기반 미니게임 웹</div>
            </div>
            <div class="top-actions">
                <button class="btn ghost" id="goHomeBtn">처음 화면</button>
                <button class="btn" id="openStatsBtn">통계</button>
                <button class="btn strong" id="openSettingsBtn">설정</button>
            </div>
        </header>

        <main>
            <section class="screen" id="startScreen">
                <div class="welcome">
                    <div class="panel hero">
                        <h1>장애 아동도 쉽게 할 수 있는<br>뇌 기능 훈련 게임</h1>
                        <p>
                            한 화면 안에서 뇌 영역을 누르고, 바로 게임을 시작하고, 통계까지 같이 볼 수 있도록 만든 간단한 미니게임 웹입니다.
                        </p>
                        <div class="hero-actions">
                            <button class="btn strong" id="startNowBtn">게임 시작하기</button>
                            <button class="btn" id="statsNowBtn">통계 보기</button>
                            <button class="btn ghost" id="directMainBtn">바로 메인 화면</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="panel">
                        <div class="section-title">
                            <h2>연결된 뇌 영역</h2>
                            <p>각 영역마다 다른 훈련 게임</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mini-grid">
                            <div class="mini-card">
                                <h3>전두엽</h3>
                                <p>계획, 판단, 집중 관련 게임</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mini-card">
                                <h3>두정엽</h3>
                                <p>공간 감각, 위치 파악 관련 게임</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mini-card">
                                <h3>측두엽</h3>
                                <p>소리 처리, 기억 관련 게임</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mini-card">
                                <h3>후두엽</h3>
                                <p>시각 처리 관련 게임</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mini-card">
                                <h3>소뇌</h3>
                                <p>반응속도, 타이밍, 운동 협응 게임</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mini-card">
                                <h3>통계</h3>
                                <p>플레이 횟수, 최고 점수, 정답률, 반응속도 저장</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="screen active" id="mainScreen">
                <div class="main-layout">
                    <div class="panel brain-panel">
                        <div class="section-title">
                            <div>
                                <h2>뇌 그림 선택 화면</h2>
                                <p>영역을 누르면 해당 게임이 바로 시작됩니다.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="brain-stage">
                            <div class="brain-wrapper">
                                <img class="brain-img" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/00/Brain_human_lateral_view.svg/1024px-Brain_human_lateral_view.svg.png" alt="뇌 그림" />

                                <svg class="brain-svg" viewBox="0 0 1100 760" preserveAspectRatio="none">
                  <defs>
                    <mask id="highlightMask">
                      <rect x="0" y="0" width="1100" height="760" fill="white"></rect>
                      <polygon id="activeMaskPolygon" points="" fill="black"></polygon>
                    </mask>
                  </defs>

                  <rect
                    id="dimOverlay"
                    x="0"
                    y="0"
                    width="1100"
                    height="760"
                    fill="rgba(30,43,63,0.55)"
                    mask="url(#highlightMask)"
                    style="display:none"
                  ></rect>

                  <polygon id="region-frontal" class="region" data-region="frontal"></polygon>
                  <polygon id="region-parietal" class="region" data-region="parietal"></polygon>
                  <polygon id="region-temporal" class="region" data-region="temporal"></polygon>
                  <polygon id="region-occipital" class="region" data-region="occipital"></polygon>
                  <polygon id="region-cerebellum" class="region" data-region="cerebellum"></polygon>
                </svg>

                                <div class="label-pill" id="brainLabel"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="brain-help">
                            <div class="tag">선택한 영역만 강조</div>
                            <div class="tag">나머지 부분은 어둡게 처리</div>
                            <div class="tag">영역 클릭 시 게임 시작</div>
                            <div class="tag">해마는 측두엽에 포함</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="right-column">
                        <div class="panel game-panel">
                            <div class="section-title">
                                <div>
                                    <h2>게임 화면</h2>
                                    <p>영역과 난이도를 고르면 바로 플레이</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="status-banner" id="gameStatusBanner"></div>

                            <div class="inline-controls">
                                <label>
                  <select class="select" id="difficultySelect">
                    <option value="easy">쉬운 게임</option>
                    <option value="hard">어려운 게임</option>
                  </select>
                </label>
                                <label>
                    <select id="hardLevelSelect" class="hidden" style="padding:6px 12px; border-radius:8px; border:1px solid var(--line); font-family:inherit;">
                        <option value="1">어려움 1단계</option>
                        <option value="2">어려움 2단계</option>
                        <option value="3">어려움 3단계</option>
                        <option value="4">어려움 4단계</option>
                        <option value="5">어려움 5단계</option>
                    </select>
                </label>
                                <button class="btn ghost" id="restartGameBtn">현재 게임 다시하기</button>
                            </div>

                            <div class="game-shell" id="gameShell">
                                <div class="center-box">
                                    <div class="game-title">영역을 먼저 선택해주세요</div>
                                    <div class="subline">
                                        전두엽, 두정엽, 측두엽, 후두엽, 소뇌 중 하나를 누르면 해당 게임이 여기에 표시됩니다.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="footer-note">
                                통계에는 플레이 횟수, 최고 점수, 정답 수, 시도 수, 정답률, 반응속도 기록이 저장됩니다.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </section>
        </main>
    </div>

    <div class="modal-backdrop" id="settingsModal">
        <div class="modal">
            <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; gap:10px; align-items:center;">
                <h3>설정</h3>
                <button class="btn ghost" id="closeSettingsBtn">닫기</button>
            </div>
            <p>
                너무 복잡하지 않게, 게임 진행에 필요한 기본 옵션만 넣었습니다.
            </p>
            <div class="modal-grid">
                <div class="setting-item">
                    <label for="soundToggle">효과 문구 표시</label>
                    <select class="select" id="soundToggle">
            <option value="on">켜기</option>
            <option value="off">끄기</option>
          </select>
